title: The Murder House Burns Down | American Horror Stories - Episode 7: "Game Over" (HQ Clip)
author: AHS Crave
comment: I'm just going to erase this entire show from my memory and focus on the real AHS universe.
This is the best scene of the episode and in the end it was just a game, just an excuse for Ryan Murphy to want to come back with this House in the future...
I wish that Violet, Tate and Constance were this season.
Kinda wish this was how Apocalypse ended. Mallory goes back to the house and the ghosts hold back Michael as she burns the house and sends Michael to hell and releases the other souls to heaven.
Ngl I loved how they had tates whistle as it burnt down
description: The iconic Murder House is set on fire & burns to the ground in "Game Over," the seventh episode of American Horror Stories (the official AHS/American Horror Story spin-off).
